      "Text": "Security update for xscreensaver",
      "Title": "Topic",
      "Type": "Summary"
    },
    {
      "Text": "The xscreensaver package was updated to fix the following security and non security issues:\n\n- CVE-2015-8025: Fixed a crash when hot-swapping monitors while locked (bsc#952062).\n- Added xscreensaver-in_signal_handler_p.patch needed for fix of signal handling.\n- Refresh xscreensaver-stars.patch.\n",
      "Title": "Details",
      "Type": "General"
